  "texts": [
    "Combining L2 regularisation with the original datasets, the paper presents offline data augmentation approaches to decrease the risk of overfitting caused by restricted data.",
    "On supplemented datasets, the DCNN (Model-2) achieves the best accuracy, which does not use max-pooling and uses Log-Mel for audio feature extraction.",
    "The achieved accuracies are 94.94% for ESC-10, 89.28% for ESC-50, and 95.37% for US8K.",
    "Environmental sound categorization difficulties are where the suggested method shines, according to the results of the experiments.",
    "The experimental study aims to investigate the use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) for ESC tasks, specifically looking at two stacked DCNN models."
